Package: yesno
Title: Ask a Custom Yes-No Question
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2017-01-29
Authors@R: c(
    person("Hadley", "Wickham", email = "hadley@rstudio.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Joe", "Thorley", email = "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", role = c("com", "cre")))
Description: Asks a custom Yes-No question with variable responses. 
    The single function is the internal yesno function from devtools 
    (modified to return TRUE if the user answers yes).
License: GPL (>= 2)
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
